<L>__{interior mccall house kitchen day}
<A>__{quincy sits at the kitchen table, writing "i am sorry" in block letters across a homemade card. his face is tight with concentration as he tries to write in a straight line. at the counter, his mom, nona, moves a cake from its store box to a cake dish. she is 30, beautiful, with effort. she smooths the frosting with a spoon. zeke, 32, with the height and ego of an nba ballplayer, enters. he laughs.}
